        "creation_date": 1500063950,
        "body": "<p>As of today, if you use Beam with release version below 2.0.0, you will have to add two hadoop dependencies in your maven pom file  for this SortValues module to work.<\/p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>add <code>hadoop-common<\/code> version 2.7.3 or later<\/li>\n<li>add <code>hadoop-mapreduce-client-core<\/code> version 2.7.3 or later.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n<p>Otherwise, you will just need to use Beam with release version >= 2.0.0.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 45111111,
        "question_id": 45069550,
        "last_edit_date": 1500064578
    }],
